Posted: June 8, 2014
Early Access Review
								For a while I was debating if I should get this game. I got a steam coupon for Plague Inc Evolved after making badges so I thought hey why not I'll buy the game since I have a coupon. After I installed the game and started playing it, I was like 'man, this is cool.' In my opinion $15.00 US dollars I have to say it's well worth it. Even though it's still in early development and the Multiplayer is still locked, the creator James is making a pretty good game. I do not have any major issues with the game but for the unlocking of the Modify Genetic Code, to make it a little more easier, not to much, but a little easier to unlock for future plagues.Which I don't know if James did fix that or not, but that just my opinion and 2 cent in with this review. I do recommend this game for if you want something different from the normal everyday games you find out there.Recommended![Rating:95/100}
